WEBVTT

01:01:08.581 --> 01:01:13.586
I really love taking naps, Dozyping!

01:01:13.586 --> 01:01:19.592
Hey! Stop right there!

01:01:19.592 --> 01:01:21.594
Huh? You startled me.

01:01:21.594 --> 01:01:23.596
You almost gave me a heart attack.

01:01:23.596 --> 01:01:28.601
Whoa! What's going on at this hour?

01:01:28.601 --> 01:01:33.606
Wait... There's no one here?

01:01:33.606 --> 01:01:38.611
It's a ghost! Aaaah!

01:01:38.611 --> 01:01:42.615
Giddy up! Giddy up! Giddy up!

01:01:42.615 --> 01:01:48.579
This is less fun than the horses in our kingdom, dozy.

01:01:48.579 --> 01:01:53.835
Isn't there anything more fun, dozy?

01:02:08.599 --> 01:02:15.565
That looks fun, dozy!

01:02:29.579 --> 01:02:42.592
Wow! The human village really has a lot of fun things, dozy.

01:02:42.592 --> 01:02:45.595
Ah, what's that sound?

01:02:45.595 --> 01:02:49.599
Huh? What? Who's there?

01:02:49.599 --> 01:02:53.603
I'm sure someone was just here...

01:02:53.603 --> 01:02:59.609
Ugh, I'm so sleepy...

01:02:59.609 --> 01:03:06.616
Isn't there somewhere comfortable to sleep, dozy...

01:03:06.616 --> 01:03:08.618
I'm heading out!

01:03:08.618 --> 01:03:11.579
Have a good day...

01:03:11.579 --> 01:03:13.581
Sarah, did you not sleep well?

01:03:13.581 --> 01:03:18.878
Yeah... I stayed up all night working on a new bread recipe.

01:03:18.878 --> 01:03:22.006
Romi, could you watch the shop later when you get back from school?

01:03:22.006 --> 01:03:24.800
I need to get some sleep.

01:03:24.800 --> 01:03:27.595
Yes, I will. I'm leaving now!

01:03:32.808 --> 01:03:34.602
Phew, I'm not late.

01:03:34.602 --> 01:03:37.813
So, I was passing through the park last night, and guess what?

01:03:37.813 --> 01:03:41.609
The stopped carousel was moving all by itself. So...

01:03:41.609 --> 01:03:45.029
Hey, are you sure someone wasn't just riding it?

01:03:46.697 --> 01:03:52.370
No, so I looked closely at the horses... and looked...

01:03:52.370 --> 01:03:54.747
There was no one there!

01:03:54.747 --> 01:03:57.583
Then suddenly, a bizarre woman's laugh!

01:03:57.583 --> 01:03:59.585
Hahahaha! Hahahaha!

01:03:59.585 --> 01:04:02.588
If you're going to lie, at least make it believable.

01:04:02.588 --> 01:04:04.590
It's not a lie!

01:04:04.590 --> 01:04:08.594
Huh? Now that you mention it, when I woke up this morning...

01:04:08.594 --> 01:04:11.597
The game console I definitely turned off was on...

01:04:11.597 --> 01:04:16.602
And in front of it, someone with long, untied hair!

01:04:16.602 --> 01:04:20.606
Aaaah!

01:04:20.606 --> 01:04:23.609
Now, now, let's start class.

01:04:23.609 --> 01:04:27.613
Yes...

01:04:27.613 --> 01:04:29.615
Mmm... Ah, this is delicious.

01:04:29.615 --> 01:04:33.995
Huh?

01:04:44.839 --> 01:04:46.882
[Yawns]

01:04:49.594 --> 01:04:51.596
Who is it?

01:04:51.596 --> 01:04:57.602
How insolent, daring to disturb a princess's sleep!

01:04:57.602 --> 01:05:02.231
Where can I go to get a good sleep, dozy...

01:05:13.618 --> 01:05:19.874
Aren't you going to sleep? Only when Your Majesty sleeps can I...

01:05:19.874 --> 01:05:21.584
Are you sleepy right now?

01:05:21.584 --> 01:05:24.587
That kid Romi is interfering with our plans!

01:05:24.587 --> 01:05:25.588
Go away!

01:05:25.588 --> 01:05:30.593
If you keep doing bad things, someday you'll have to pay a big price.

01:05:30.593 --> 01:05:37.600
Be quiet!

01:05:37.600 --> 01:05:39.602
Aha! There she is.

01:05:39.602 --> 01:05:44.607
Right, if it's Dozyping's magic...

01:05:44.607 --> 01:05:51.030
I'm just going to sleep right here, dozy.

01:05:57.620 --> 01:06:02.583
Yo! Wake up! Wake up!

01:06:02.583 --> 01:06:06.587
How can a princess sleep on the street?

01:06:06.587 --> 01:06:10.591
I know a place that's just perfect for you.

01:06:10.591 --> 01:06:16.430
Alright, should we take them out now?

01:06:21.602 --> 01:06:24.605
This is the place, dozy.

01:06:26.607 --> 01:06:29.610
Huh?

01:06:36.617 --> 01:06:40.579
Guys, are you okay?

01:06:40.579 --> 01:06:45.584
Huh? Everyone is sleeping?

01:06:47.545 --> 01:06:49.171
It's a Teenieping alarm, chu!

01:06:58.764 --> 01:07:03.602
That is the Princess Teenieping of the Sleeping Kingdom, Dozyping, pony!

01:07:03.602 --> 01:07:08.607
What, this will be an easy catch!

01:07:08.607 --> 01:07:14.613
Oh no! Dozyping is snoring, pony!

01:07:14.613 --> 01:07:17.616
Then because of that snoring sound...?

01:07:17.616 --> 01:07:26.584
Let's catch her quickly! Time to transform, chu!

01:07:26.584 --> 01:07:32.590
Open! Princess Pact!

01:07:32.590 --> 01:07:36.594
Wake up, chu!

01:07:36.594 --> 01:07:39.597
Let's evacuate outside for now!

01:07:39.597 --> 01:07:44.602
Dozyping likes to stay up all night playing without sleeping, pony...

01:07:44.602 --> 01:07:48.606
So she has a bad habit of snoring anywhere during the day.

01:07:48.606 --> 01:07:53.444
Everyone around who hears that sound falls asleep, sappun!

01:07:55.070 --> 01:07:59.450
It seems much stronger than my dad's snoring.

01:07:59.450 --> 01:08:01.619
How do we catch her?

01:08:01.619 --> 01:08:03.579
Ah! That's it!

01:08:03.579 --> 01:08:06.582
How about earplugs, ping?

01:08:06.582 --> 01:08:12.588
Earplugs, pingereureu!

01:08:12.588 --> 01:08:15.591
Now, try making a sound.

01:08:15.591 --> 01:08:18.594
Aaaaah!

01:08:20.596 --> 01:08:22.598
Romi, let's transform, chu!

01:08:22.598 --> 01:08:23.599
Yeah!

01:08:23.599 --> 01:08:31.607
Open! Princess Pact!

01:08:31.607 --> 01:08:36.195
Noble love's Heartsping Time!

01:08:48.791 --> 01:08:53.170
Princess Fancyheart of love that fills the heart!

01:08:57.508 --> 01:08:58.592
Good.

01:09:02.346 --> 01:09:04.098
Piripiri Catchling!

01:09:06.267 --> 01:09:10.604
Don't tell me... The pact can't hear me.

01:09:12.439 --> 01:09:15.609
Wake up, Dozyping!

01:09:15.609 --> 01:09:21.699
What? Is the meal ready, dozy?

01:09:21.699 --> 01:09:24.618
Dozyping! You stayed up all night playing again, didn't you, pony!

01:09:25.578 --> 01:09:27.663
You're Bonnyping.

01:09:27.663 --> 01:09:33.586
There are so many fun things here. More than my kingdom...

01:09:35.796 --> 01:09:37.590
Don't fall asleep!

01:09:39.592 --> 01:09:44.805
That snoring sound is coming through the earplugs, pony...

01:09:46.015 --> 01:09:47.600
Wake up, Bonnyping!

01:09:47.600 --> 01:09:50.603
The sound is even louder than before!

01:09:50.603 --> 01:09:54.607
First, we have to stop her from snoring, chu!

01:09:54.607 --> 01:09:59.612
Love's Magic, chu!

01:09:59.612 --> 01:10:02.239
It failed, chu!

01:10:06.243 --> 01:10:09.163
At this rate, everyone will fall asleep, Arung...

01:10:09.163 --> 01:10:11.373
Graceping!

01:10:20.633 --> 01:10:24.470
Huh? Great job, Graceping!

01:10:24.470 --> 01:10:32.603
This is nothing, sappun.

01:10:32.603 --> 01:10:40.611
Graceping! I'll help you!

01:10:43.113 --> 01:10:46.492
Guys!

01:10:46.492 --> 01:10:51.705
Ah, no, I can't hold out any longer...

01:10:55.084 --> 01:10:58.170
This is a lot harder than I thought.

01:10:58.712 --> 01:11:00.214
What do I do??

01:11:02.091 --> 01:11:04.301
Man! I'm telling you it's real!

01:11:04.301 --> 01:11:06.595
Yo! Can't you hear me?

01:11:06.595 --> 01:11:10.307
Huh? Are we thinking the same thing?

01:11:11.809 --> 01:11:13.811
Hey! Are you going to keep pretending not to hear me?

01:11:13.811 --> 01:11:15.062
I'll give it back when I'm done!

01:11:15.062 --> 01:11:18.607
What did you say?

01:11:18.607 --> 01:11:26.615
I won't let you off this time!

01:11:27.658 --> 01:11:31.120
Love's Magic Ring!

01:11:39.753 --> 01:11:41.255
Do it now Princess!

01:11:42.965 --> 01:11:45.592
Piripiri Catchling!

01:11:48.470 --> 01:11:50.723
Into the Princess Cube!

01:11:59.606 --> 01:12:02.568
Princess Teenieping, Dozyping, Catch!

01:12:02.568 --> 01:12:05.612
[Yawn]

01:12:05.612 --> 01:12:11.618
I'm going to sleep again, dozy.

01:12:11.618 --> 01:12:21.587
I slept well for the first time in a while.

01:12:21.587 --> 01:12:24.590
Dozyping! You shouldn't sleep now.

01:12:24.590 --> 01:12:26.592
You won't be able to sleep tonight.

01:12:26.592 --> 01:12:29.595
That's right, dozy.

01:12:34.558 --> 01:12:38.896
Tsk Tsk Tsk Tsk Tsk! That's why I told you to sleep at night.

01:12:44.068 --> 01:12:46.070
Eclipseping.

01:12:46.070 --> 01:12:47.946
[End Credits]